Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:35.42,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Đây là thú ăn thịt thì có!{I thought it was curry, \Nbut it was actually a predator.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:37.99,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Thật chẳng hiểu mình nói gì nữa luôn.{I don't even know what I'm saying.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:43.38,Noichuyen,TAMA,0,0,0,,Mình dùng nhầm nguyên liệu sao?{Did I use the wrong special ingredient?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:47.17,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Chị cho bột zombie vào đấy à?{What did you put in this, zombie powder?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:56.22,Noichuyen,TAMA,0,0,0,,Chả còn cách nào.{Looks like I've only got one choice.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:59.00,Noichuyen,TAMA,0,0,0,,Đành ra ngoài mua nguyên liệu mới vậy.{I have to go out and buy more ingredients.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:00.42,Noichuyen,TAMA,0,0,0,,Đi không, ngài cáo?{Want to come, Mr. Fox?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:03.37,Noichuyen,TAMA,0,0,0,,Mà quần áo đó quá cỡ rồi.{Your clothes are too big for you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:07.67,Noichuyen,TAMA,0,0,0,,Mặc bộ này vào đi.{Before we leave, put on these \Nclothes that are just your size.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:09.64,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn nha.{Okay. Thanks.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:17.89,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Đây là quần áo con gái mà!{These are girl clothes!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.89,0:19:19.97,Noichuyen,TAMA,0,0,0,,Là quần áo búp bê đó, nya!{They're doll clothes.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:25.61,Noichuyen,TAMA,0,0,0,,Lúc thế này thì phải rưng rưng nước mắt rồi nói,{By the way, in this situation, a pro would \Nlook up with tears in his eyes and say:}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.61,0:19:29.04,Noichuyen,TAMA,0,0,0,,"Không phải thế này! Tui là trai mờ!"{"This isn't right! I'm a boy!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:30.60,Noichuyen,TAMA,0,0,0,,Nào nào, làm đi, làm đi.{Come on, do it, do it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:34.12,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Bà chị quái gở.{This lady's weird.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:49.01,Noichuyen,TAMA,0,0,0,,Không ngờ cậu vẫn dám mặc thế ra đường đó.{I didn't think you'd actually come dressed like that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:51.77,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Cản em đi chứ!{You should've stopped me!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:53.15,Noichuyen,TAMA,0,0,0,,Biến thái!{Pervert.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:55.15,Noichuyen,KOHINA,0,0,0,,Biến thái!{Pervert.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:05.58,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Chị ơi, nắm tay đi không lạc nhau đó.{Lady, I'll hold your hand so you \Ndon't get separated from us.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:08.78,Noichuyen,KOHINA,0,0,0,,Tên em không phải là chị.{My name is not "Lady."}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:11.85,Noichuyen,KOHINA,0,0,0,,Em là Ichimatsu Kohina.{I am Ichimatsu Kohina.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:17.99,Noichuyen,KOHINA,0,0,0,,Mà em không muốn đi cạnh một tên con trai mặc đồ gái giữa ban ngày.{Also, I don't want to walk next to a boy \Nwho cross-dresses in broad daylight.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:21.34,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Em đâu có thích thế này chứ!{It's not like I wanted to wear this.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:23.20,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Chị ích kỉ quá đó.{You're mean, lady.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.87,Noichuyen,KOHINA,0,0,0,,Em là Kohina.{I am Kohina.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:33.24,Noichuyen,KOHINA,0,0,0,,Búp bê bị ảnh hưởng bởi cả những tên con trai thích giả gái. {em không hiểu rõ câu này lắm, dịch lại dùm đi}{Dolls are repulsed by older cross-dressers \Nwho pretend to be children, too.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:38.35,Noichuyen,KOHINA,0,0,0,,Kokkuri-san sẽ thế này bao lâu nữa?{How long will Kokkuri-san remain a child?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:43.96,Noichuyen,KOHINA,0,0,0,,Anh ấy sẽ không còn nhớ mình là ai sao?{Will he never remember who I am?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.44,0:20:49.32,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Chị ốm à?{Are you not feeling well?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:50.81,Noichuyen,KOHINA,0,0,0,,Hả?{What?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:54.79,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Trông chị hơi xuống sắc.{You seemed a little down.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:08.98,Noichuyen,KOHINA,0,0,0,,Không thể nào. Búp bê là bất hoại.{That's impossible. Dolls are unperturbed.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:10.81,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Thật à?{Really?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:13.53,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Chị ổn là được rồi...{As long as you're fine...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:16.75,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Búp bê ư?{Dolls?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:28.72,Noichuyen,KOHINA,0,0,0,,Dù Kokkuri-san có ở hình dạng nào,{Kokkuri-san may be getting his \Nkicks out of acting like a child,}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:33.01,Noichuyen,KOHINA,0,0,0,,Thì anh ấy vẫn là Kokkuri-san.{but he's still the same Kokkuri-san.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:41.67,Noichuyen,TAMA,0,0,0,,Mà thấy thèm nước hồi xuân quá.{Anyway, I wish I could've had \Nsome of that water of youth.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:44.18,Noichuyen,TAMA,0,0,0,,Mỗi tội nguồn cung khó kiếm lắm.{Supplies are low, so it's difficult to get.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:48.89,Noichuyen,TAMA,0,0,0,,Vả lại, giờ hàng nhái của nó cũng nhiều lắm.{On top of that, its popularity \Nhas spawned tons of knockoffs.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:52.61,Noichuyen,TAMA,0,0,0,,Uống vào cũng chỉ có tác dụng vài ngày.{The knockoffs are low-quality fakes \Nthat wear off after a few days.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:54.77,Noichuyen,TAMA,0,0,0,,Mua chỉ vô ích.{I'm not interested in purchasing those.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.68,0:21:57.33,Noichuyen,TAMA,0,0,0,,Hả?{Huh?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.57,0:22:12.49,Noichuyen,TAMA,0,0,0,,Có vẻ như anh mua phải hàng nhái rồi.{Looks like you purchased one of those knockoffs.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.95,0:22:22.44,Noichuyen,NARRATION,0,0,0,,Cú sốc khi thấy mình trong gương khiến Kokkuri-san trở lại bình thường.{The shock of seeing his own reflection \Nreturned Kokkuri-san to his senses.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.87,0:22:25.28,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Hả? Cái-cái gì?{Huh? Wh-What?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:27.16,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Sao tôi lại mặc thế này?{Why am I dressed like this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.16,0:22:29.60,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Chuyện gì đây?{Seriously, what's going on?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:32.75,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Nghe đây!{Now, listen!}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.10,0:22:35.72,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Ai đó đã bán cho tôi nước hồi xuân giả!{Someone sold me fake water of youth!}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:42.34,Noichuyen,NARRATION,0,0,0,,Kokkuri-san đã đâm đơn khiếu nại các trung tâm tiêu dùng.{Kokkuri-san furiously submitted a \Ncomplaint to the consumer center.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.03,0:22:38.13,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Tôi nói là...{I }{\i1}{told}{\i0}{ you...}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.26,0:22:41.39,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Anh nghe không đó?{Are you listening?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:44.87,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Hoàn tiền lại, rõ chưa?{I can return it, right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.87,0:22:45.96,Noichuyen,KOKKURI,0,0,0,,Rõ chưa?{Right?!}
